{"word":"G2664 - καταπαύω - katapaúō - kat-ap-ow'-o - Cease","slug":"G2664","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταπαύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>katapaúō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kat-ap-ow'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Cease"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - katapauo&#x0304;</b> - <i>kat-ap-ow'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G3973\">G3973</a>; to <i>settle down</i>, that is, (literally) to <i>colonize</i>, or (figuratively) to (<i>cause to</i>) <i>desist:</i> - cease, (give) rest (-rain)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2663\">G2663</a>"}]}